-- Goldman Sachs Being Investigated in Currency Probe, Filing Shows
-- B y   G a v i n   F i n c h
-- 2013-11-07T11:27:48Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-11-07/goldman-sachs-being-investigated-in-currency-probe-filing-shows.html
Goldman Sachs Group Inc. disclosed in
a quarterly filing that it’s cooperating with an investigation
into  currency trading .  The firm’s filing today added currencies and commodities to
a list of financial products and related activities that are
subject to investigation.  Regulators around the world have been looking into whether
banks have rigged currency rates.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Gavin Finch in London at 
 gfinch@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Christine Harper at 
 charper@bloomberg.net  